How are ratings calculated?

4.0 out of 5 stars Value for money compared to Eveready
Reviewed in Australia on 18 July 2023
Style: AAASize: 20Verified Purchase
The product like other Duracell coppertop batteries is as good as expected - that is, they are better than most other brands. I like the fact these are pretty good value for money as far as alkaline batteries go and they are at least more trustworthy and thus, dependable than "no-name" brands or even some other with known brands. The main thing is whether they will leak and that is only dependable on time and the environment (heat, humidity, etc) and this is an unknown as the product is supplied in nicely heat shrink plastic (4 to a set x 5) in a sealed cardboard box which all helps to prevent the ingress of moisture. All cells tested at the rated voltage of 1.5v per cell. No idea how long they will last in my different products which has different current drains.
